question: How many people lived in Odense Municipality, Denmark on July 1, 2022?
asked_question_translated: Hvor mange mennesker bodde i Odense kommune i Danmark 1. juli 2022?
answer: Den 1. juli 2022 bodde det cirka 205,149 mennesker i Odense kommune i Danmark.
answer_translated_eng: On 1 July 2022, there were approximately 205,149 people living in Odense Municipality in Denmark.
